    <briefdescription>
<para>CRC context structure. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This structure holds the state of the CRC calculation, including the type of CRC being calculated, the current state, the polynomial, the initial seed value, and the result of the CRC calculation. </para>
